DiagLOVProvider
public class SampleAppLOVProviderCustomBean
extends SampleAppLOVProvider

A Sample App LOV Provider. This is the same as the SampleAppLOVProvider class except that for illustration purposes, each row of the LOV data is represented using a custom Java bean.
